  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The protagonist, who has taken a job as a special cleaner, goes to his first cleaning site with his seniors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Witnessing the scene of a gruesome death, he begins to feel something that he has never felt before.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >He begins to feel the presence of something he has never felt before.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A collection of short stories in 3 parts</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 endings + several extra endings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keyboard and mouse controls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Operation Method</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Movement</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WASD</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left click</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TAB key</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Menu screen</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137220/extras/09b117a16d5e24b90dc632ccb4c8f0db.avif?t=1740138212\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137220/extras_big/09b117a16d5e24b90dc632ccb4c8f0db.avif?t=1740138212 width=800 height=408 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137220/extras/c543fa199f5a3a6d7b853e174d88db03.avif?t=1740138212\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137220/extras_big/c543fa199f5a3a6d7b853e174d88db03.avif?t=1740138212 width=800 height=408 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137220/extras/89b71bc363f15804ce19578f49d3b218.avif?t=1740138212\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137220/extras_big/89b71bc363f15804ce19578f49d3b218.avif?t=1740138212 width=800 height=408 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game contains elements of a walking simulator in which you move around the map while checking items.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137220/extras/730807c92863782f75fd475b4f6b5a5c.avif?t=1740138212\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137220/extras_big/730807c92863782f75fd475b4f6b5a5c.avif?t=1740138212 width=800 height=412 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137220/extras/239b0a681b529d703c00955103e254b9.avif?t=1740138212\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137220/extras_big/239b0a681b529d703c00955103e254b9.avif?t=1740138212 width=800 height=410 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is a fictional story that has nothing to do with any actual incidents or accidents, although it does contain some cruel expressions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are welcome to distribute the game in real life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No prior notification is required, but please include the URL of the store page in the summary section of the distribution page.</p>",
